text: Ajimudaoro Aladesanmi I was a Yoruban Oba who reigned as Ewi of Ado Ekiti in Nigeria from 1886 until 1910. He was the father of Daniel Aladesanmi II. == References == Ajimudaora Category:Nigerian traditional rulers Category:Nigerian royalty Category:Yoruba monarchs Category:People from Ekiti State
title: Ajimudaoro Aladesanmi I
